Package: predatortune
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.10), python3-gi, gir1.2-adw-1, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, python3-gi-cairo, lm-sensors, nbfc-linux
Maintainer: Madhav <madhav@meowdev>
Description: Fan control GUI for Acer Predator laptops on Linux
 PredatorTune is a GTK4/Adwaita fan control application for Acer Predator
 laptops running Linux. It provides real-time temperature monitoring,
 manual fan speed control, and preset profiles similar to PredatorSense
 on Windows. Uses NBFC (Notebook Fan Control) as the backend.
Homepage: https://github.com/0xshubhs/predatur
